This is a cracking thriller starring a wealth of stars from British film and television. A ruthless kidnapper and blackmailer has abducted a young boy. After imprisoning the child in a deserted house, the kidnapper gives him a toy golly for comfort. But hidden inside the golly is time bomb which is set to explode at ten the following morning.
